{"tid":704673,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"美斯拒認完美球員：仲要練12碼","createTime":"2018-06-16T14:55:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-17T05:56:07.000Z","uid":49724,"like":118,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"305a9d74cf84ae36485e73e7b75d578d75f0e1f7","tid":704673,"uid":49724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T14:55:54.000Z","msg":"阿根廷球星美斯被喻為史上最強球員，不過這名巴塞隆拿核心直言自己並非完美，直言自己仍有不足的地方，特別是在處理極刑方面仍需努力。<br />\n莫迪歷追平蘇加6奪克羅地亞足球先生<br />\n<br />\n美斯是不少人心目中的球王，但他接受訪問是謙稱自己仍非一名完美的球員，特別指出自己主射12碼方面的問題：「我希望成為完美的球員，但始終仍有要改進的地方。什麼方面？12碼吧，我要多練習一些。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f78f9057e8ba2e45e331e64c29786c0c20b9f1b2","tid":704673,"uid":58552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T14:56:19.000Z","msg":"好波"},{"pid":"a9b4d46c903ef7103c61b58b31049477a6053a21","tid":704673,"uid":73356,"like":125,"dislike":0,"score":125,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T14:57:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/16/225704_cbcdc971c1042ea233a0d22d23afcb57.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F16%2F225704_cbcdc971c1042ea233a0d22d23afcb57.jpeg&h=d18008b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/16/225708_acf057eca917d9b6d217e9f7eb9a921f.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F16%2F225708_acf057eca917d9b6d217e9f7eb9a921f.jpeg&h=1b8c080c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/iceland.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/iceland.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/iceland.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/iceland.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5571af18c7b27f0e20c848b38a3dca49e94ecbc","tid":704673,"uid":72946,"like":34,"dislike":1,"scor